{"tid":547361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我們不一樣","createTime":"2018-02-01T11:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T11:08:19.000Z","uid":165196,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b822c83159234cc5653b05871ffdba2347e33b32","tid":547361,"uid":165196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">這麼多年的兄弟<br />\n有誰比我更瞭解你<br />\n太多太多不容易<br />\n磨平了歲月和脾氣<br />\n時間轉眼就過去<br />\n這身後不散的筵席<br />\n只因為我們還在<br />\n心留在原地<br />\n張開手 需要多大的勇氣<br />\n這片天 你我一起撐起<br />\n更努力 只為了我們想要的明天<br />\n好好的 這份情好好珍惜<br />\n我們不一樣<br />\n每個人都有不同的境遇<br />\n我們在這裡<br />\n在這裡等你</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7384af316776d51012fc9664681603b4995870a","tid":547361,"uid":70429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"支那狗聽支那歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾好聽"},{"pid":"7852c7cc59143dd8c7ee676558cb7c1b2f690cfc","tid":547361,"uid":165196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7384af316776d51012fc9664681603b4995870a","tid":547361,"uid":70429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"支那狗聽支那歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾好聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"对<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}